@startuml
title checkPermission - 예외 기반 방식

actor OuterContext as "OuterContext\n(외부 호출자)"
participant PermissionController
participant PermissionService
participant PermissionRepository
Entity PermissionPolicy
Entity ManagerAssignment
participant ExceptionHandler as "GlobalExceptionHandler\n(@ControllerAdvice)"

OuterContext -> PermissionController : GET /internal/permissions?userId=..&boardId=..&action=..
PermissionController -> PermissionService : checkPermission(userId, boardId, action)

PermissionService -> PermissionRepository : findByBoardId(boardId)
PermissionRepository -> PermissionService : PermissionPolicy
PermissionService -> PermissionPolicy : can(userId, action)
PermissionPolicy -> ManagerAssignment : hasPermission(userId, action)
alt 권한 있음
  ManagerAssignment --> PermissionPolicy : 반환 없음 (성공)
  PermissionPolicy --> PermissionService : 반환 없음 (성공)
  PermissionService --> PermissionController : HTTP 200 OK
  PermissionController --> OuterContext : HTTP 200 OK
else 권한 없음
  ManagerAssignment --> ExceptionHandler : throw ForbiddenException
  ExceptionHandler --> OuterContext : HTTP 403 Forbidden
end

@enduml